m\": 686, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"four Olympic champions\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I told (her coach) Rocco and Tatjana in 2019 that she'd do what she's doing.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her coach\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"Rocco\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 798}, {\"ngram\": \"Tatjana\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's a lovely person.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lovely person\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's too good for these girls, she's like Phelps.\\\"\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999643978306, \"rank\": 3.560131763094666e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these girls\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos was able to take a gold medal off of Phelps himself, but says that he wasn't ready for what would come after that.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 972, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999643978306, \"rank\": 3.560131763094666e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 964}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He recalled what Phelps said to him inLondon 2012: \\\"\\\"I am passing the torch to you now, enjoy the moment.\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999643978306, \"rank\": 3.560131763094666e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to be watching your career.\\\"\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your career\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos believes that he wasn't 'supposed' to win that race in 2012 but feels that 2016 was a different story.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1308, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1205}, {\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"a different story\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He feels that losing to someone who was subsequently sanctioned for doping is a mark on the sport.\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1341}, {\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"a mark\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wasn't supposed to win that race,\\\" he said of London \\\"If we had swum that race a hundred times, if we could replay it like a Fifa game, Phelps would win it 97, 98 times.\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1459, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.999999999908141, \"rank\": 5.549818672560528e-11, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999643978306, \"rank\": 3.560131763094666e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"a Fifa game\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"98 times\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then again, in 2016, I'd win that 200m freestyle 95 out of a hundred times.\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that 200m freestyle\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"a hundred times\", \"from\": 1643, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I should have two golds and two silvers.\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two golds\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"two silvers\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That race still haunts me.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1727, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That race\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I hate myself for that race.\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, the gold medallist (Sun Yang) is a drug cheat.\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1809, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1783, \"end\": 1791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yang\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the gold medallist\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1781}, {\"ngram\": \"a drug cheat\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1808}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's been banned for doping.\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doping\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, swimming is full of politics.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1852}, {\"ngram\": \"politics\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His country is a lot bigger than South Africa.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1907, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999997489795, \"rank\": 2.4952676384656754e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His country\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It would take a lot for the authorities to strip him and hand me the gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1940}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1960}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Le Clos believes that swimming's Olympic focus means that many forget what happens between the games.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Le Clos\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming's Olympic focus\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2044}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have always wanted to go down as the best.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Have I under-achieved?\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have over-achieved.\", \"from\": 2174, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us play this back.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From 2012 I over-achieved.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I beat Phelps.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2253, \"end\": 2259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999643978306, \"rank\": 3.560131763094666e-08, \"text\": \"Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had the world at my feet.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2276}, {\"ngram\": \"my feet\", \"from\": 2280, \"to\": 2287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I followed up by winning double gold at the 2013 world championships.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"double gold\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2325}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2013 world championships\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2014 Commonwealth Games I won seven medals.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2014 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"seven medals\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2015 at the world champs I won gold and silver.\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world champs\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At Rio 2016 the silver should have been gold.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2506, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the silver\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2017 I was world champ again and at the 2018 Commonwealth Games I won five medals.\", \"from\": 2507, \"to\": 2592, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 2546, \"to\": 2573}, {\"ngram\": \"five medals\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have also won 20 world short-course championship medals, the second most in the history of swimming.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"20 world short-course championship medals\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Ryan Lochte has won more and I need three more medals (or two gold) to overtake him as short-course swimming GOAT.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2701, \"end\": 2712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ryan Lochte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Lochte\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three more medals\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2754}, {\"ngram\": \"two gold\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"short-course swimming GOAT\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then you have Phelps and myself as swimming's two GOATS.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2872, \"entiti